}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "7000-0617-00" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The RAM chip shown would appear to be a M12L64164A-7T (8 MiB)..
Default settings (including the SSID, which does seem to be used [per '''WiGLE''']) are per the FCC manual. They may be inaccurate.
